overview.en: ASC is committed to using the economic reconstruction of real estate industry, will be used by the company system to establish ecological transition of production relations to the chain through the economy, with real estate ecological chain reshaping public interests above everything else, for each individual to share to the real estate value of the whole industry chain.
overview.zh: ASC 致力于利用通证经济重构不动产行业，将从前由公司制度建立的生产关系过度到链上生态型通证经济，用公心重塑链上房地产生态，让每一个个体都能分享到不动产整个产业链的价值。
